      "content": "exactly. it feels like a logical fallacy that we're forced to participate in. if the outcome of living or dying is mathematically neutral in an indifferent universe, then deciding to stop is just as valid as deciding to continue. isn't it more honest to just accept that staying isn't a requirement?",
